{"type": "article", "id": 16560, "title": "山石软泥灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-26T06:50:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000345JqwB2A75ktEPi1xF.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t越来越的设计团队喜欢开发混凝土的设计美感，台湾的 tripleliving 团队曾经创造了一种软水泥材质，让水泥温和柔软。而这盏山石软泥灯则是在其基础上的再创新，他们保留了硅胶材质和水泥纹路，用手工灌制的方式调配透光比例，让光芒能够透出来，改变了原本印象中的机械冰冷的水泥。而圆锥体的外形像一座小山，使这盏灯有了沉静内敛的气质，让人静下心来观察纹路。产品目前在众筹，<a href=\"http://www.zeczec.com/projects/tripleliving-ms\" target=\"_blank\">这里是众筹链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143751fDPeISs5L32Abd1T.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"423\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143752gjWY1yzA9lSBpCiM.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"423\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143753jUKWhcDMQHE8F2np.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"423\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143753dPE90uvF7ij6nSce.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"423\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.65076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}